Code preview of table METADATA

if exists (select 1
from sys.sysreferences r join sys.sysobjects o on (o.id = r.constid and o.type = 'F')
where r.fkeyid = object_id('METADATA') and o.name = 'FK_UNITS_PROCCESS_SOURCES')
alter table METADATA
drop constraint FK_UNITS_PROCCESS_SOURCES
go

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('METADATA')
and type = 'U')
drop table METADATA
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: METADATA */
/*==============================================================*/
create table METADATA (
SOURCE varchar(20) not null,
COLNAME varchar(50) not null,
ORDERID int not null,
SQLTYPE varchar(100) not null,
FORMAT varchar(50) null,
SOURCEPARENT varchar(20) null,
COLNAMEPARENT varchar(50) null,
ORDERIDPARENT int null,
constraint PK_METADATA primary key nonclustered (SOURCE, COLNAME)
)
go

declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'Registro de metadatos de las fuentes de datos,
Orden ',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'METADATA'
go

declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'formato de Salida, utilizado en fechas y numeros',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'METADATA', 'column', 'FORMAT'
go

alter table METADATA
add constraint FK_UNITS_PROCCESS_SOURCES foreign key (SOURCE)
references SOURCE (SOURCE)
go
